{"tw": {"4314240": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "OnlyVans", "steam_appid": 4314240, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>愉悅之路已為你敞開</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/2cd87a3b7f6f29f35841f7d34162e026.poster.avif?t=1771803083\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/2cd87a3b7f6f29f35841f7d34162e026.webm?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/2cd87a3b7f6f29f35841f7d34162e026.mp4?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OnlyVans 將廂型車生活的自由與成人內容創作的快感完美融合。你是一名流浪攝影師，懷揣著一個明確的目標：在這個美麗且充滿風格化的開放世界中，搜尋那些隱藏在各處、最狂野、最另類的（Kinky）角色——並將短暫的邂逅轉化為令人難忘的內容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這不僅僅是拍照。 這關乎好奇心、化學反應以及誘惑的藝術。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/13ddaf26ec222d7823a24e582f163e72.poster.avif?t=1771803083\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/13ddaf26ec222d7823a24e582f163e72.webm?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/13ddaf26ec222d7823a24e582f163e72.mp4?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 搜尋。誘惑。拍攝。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這裡，慾望不會主動找上門——你需要去狩獵它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這個世界充滿了隱藏在人群中的 NPC，每個人都有自己的情緒、底線和秘密渴望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狩獵</strong> 漫遊在開闊的道路上，發掘隱藏的地點、離網區域和意想不到的邂逅。有些角色渴望被發現，而有些則需要你的說服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/780de3a8ecc001745144100b2831f5e4.poster.avif?t=1771803083\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/780de3a8ecc001745144100b2831f5e4.webm?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/780de3a8ecc001745144100b2831f5e4.mp4?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>誘惑</strong> 參與以說服為核心的互動系統。讀懂他們的情緒，謹慎遣詞用句，送出正確的禮物，慢慢解鎖他們真正的愛好。從害羞的調情到大膽的露骨表現，每個人的反應都各不相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拍攝時段</strong> 一旦建立了信任，氣氛就會變得親密。切換到第一人稱攝影模式來取景大膽的照片，探索多種姿勢和場景，捕捉那些充滿冒險、私人且回饋感十足的瞬間。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/538a56faf5acb41309ebfefb784f5686.poster.avif?t=1771803083\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/538a56faf5acb41309ebfefb784f5686.webm?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314240/extras/538a56faf5acb41309ebfefb784f5686.mp4?t=1771803083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚐 打造你的移動遊樂場</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的廂型車不僅僅是交通工具——它是你的家、你的工作室，有時甚至是……更多。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定義你的內飾，將普通的露營車打造成迷人且私密的空間</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增添氛圍燈、床位和情趣道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升廂型車的格調，以吸引更大膽、要求更多的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正確的氣氛能開啟言語無法打開的大門。</p></li